query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as total_count, 
       COUNT(DISTINCT prefecture) as prefecture_count,
       COUNT(DISTINCT city) as city_count,
       COUNT(DISTINCT propertyType) as property_type_count
FROM aggregated_real_estate_data;
